astra-theme is a fork of the @myst-theme/book site theme. The following files in
this repository are derived from @myst-theme/book (with local modifications —
ASTRA integration, deduplication, and performance cleanups) and remain under
the MIT License:

  app/root.tsx
  app/entry.client.tsx
  app/entry.server.tsx
  app/types.ts
  app/routes/**
  app/components/**
  app/utils/**
  styles/app.css
  styles/grid-system.css
  server.js
  remix.config.prod.js, remix.config.dev.js
  tailwind.config.js, tsconfig.json, remix.env.d.ts, .eslintrc.js

The theme also depends on the published @myst-theme/* npm packages
(@myst-theme/site, @myst-theme/providers, myst-to-react, etc.), each under their
own licenses (MIT), resolved at install time.

The ASTRA-specific code — app/astra/**, styles/astra.css, packages/store-types,
and this repository's configuration and documentation — is original work under
the BSD 3-Clause License.

